nal maturation of patrol officers in 'Laconia' (a pseudonym) . . . . His discussions of [the policemen's] moral development are threaded through with analytically suggestive formulations that bespeak a wisdom very rarely encountered in reports of sociological research."—Michael Banton, Times Literary Supplement  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Apr 2022) 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780226218663423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780226218663/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles